title: Hunt for missing MH370 flight ends in mystery
text:
Hunt for missing MH370 flight ends in mystery 4:37pm BST - 02:02
The underwater search for missing Malaysia Airlines flight MH370 has ended with no conclusive evidence to the airliner's fate, four years after it disappeared over the Indian Ocean in the world's biggest aviation mystery. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
